Loris Karius' agent, Florian Goll, on reports he could return to #LFC in Jan. <br />
<br />
&quot;Complete nonsense! I wonder where such things come from. This news is absolutely untrue. Loris is on loan to Besiktas for 2 years, that's the situation.&quot; No intention to end this loan contract.&quot;
